-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh CLB HAGL Hu\u1ef3nh Mau \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 V\u0103n Thanh v\u00e0 v\u1eabn theo d\u00f5i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL tiet lo doi bong nuoc ngoai muon co Van Thanh hinh anh\" title=\"HAGL ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 V\u0103n Thanh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/24/HAGL-tiet-lo-doi-bong-nuoc-ngoai-muon-co-Van-Thanh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n Thanh v\u00e0 V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, V\u0103n Thanh hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf CLB HAGL c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0110TQG d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang. V\u1edbi s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ngo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m SEA Games 29, V\u0103n Thanh t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi sang Serbia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i CLB FK Vojvodina, song&nbsp;c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua khi anh ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T U22 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 SEA Games. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ph\u00eda HAGL \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh CLB HAGL Hu\u1ef3nh Mau kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn tha thi\u1ebft mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh. H\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i khi anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ngo\u00e0i V\u0103n Thanh th\u00ec V\u0103n To\u00e0n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-cap-nhat-tin-moi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tuan-anh-168-183219.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/hagl-cap-nhat-tin-moi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tuan-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-cap-nhat-tin-moi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tuan-anh-168-183219.html\">HAGL c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tin m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tin m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"651","checkdouble":"183220"},{"date":"14:35 31/03","title":"S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c kh\u1ee7ng","typ