          <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"So tien thuong cho DT U23 Viet Nam da vuot moc 50 ty dong hinh anh\" title=\"S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed1c 50 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/So-tien-thuong-cho-DT-U23-Viet-Nam-da-vuot-moc-50-ty-dong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed1c 50 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00c1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo, nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea1nh tay th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t nam VFF v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 30/3 th\u00ec sau k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed1c 50 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 62 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 51.478.300.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, VFF c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb kh\u00e1c t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng hi\u1ec7n v\u1eadt, trong khi 17 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5. VFF cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ec1n cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c to l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u01a1i d\u1eady ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t v\u1eeba l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i chung c\u00f3 th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-u23-tai-dt-viet-nam-ke-thang-hoa-nguoi-that-vong-168-183004.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/sao-u23-tai-dt-viet-nam-ke-thang-hoa-nguoi-that-vong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-u23-tai-dt-viet-nam-ke-thang-hoa-nguoi-that-vong-168-183004.html\">Sao U23 t\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: K\u1ebb th\u0103ng hoa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 14 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"650","checkdouble":"183221"},{"date":"15:06 31/03","title":"HAGL gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1edfng u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/hagl-giau-bai-cong-phuong-xuan-truong-ue-oai-truoc-tran-gap-nam-dinh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margi