ont-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, anh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap m\u00ecnh b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesse Lingard ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jesse Lingard \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/manchester-united-1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U</strong></span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ra s\u00e2n 38 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thi dau bung no, Jesse Lingard phat bieu ve MU hinh anh\" title=\"Thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/11/Thi-dau-bung-no,-Jesse-Lingard-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lingard \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n 26 l\u1ea7n, ghi 8 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lingard c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 8 b\u00e0n m\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Lingard c\u00f2n gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Italia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup, \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Tottenham \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u1ede Premier League, d\u00f9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p song Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n Lingard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lingard ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/jesse-lingard-43829.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Jesse Lingard </strong></span>ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, anh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap m\u00ecnh b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y: \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho\u00a0 Leicester, Derby, Brighton v\u00e0 Birmingham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch l\u0169y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard cua M.U\" title=\"Lingard cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/the-he-vang-MU-92-la-dong-luc-cho-cac-sao-tre-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Mourinho, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 trao cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb \u00f4ng \u1ea5y b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d, Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/205508-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"644","checkdouble":"183216"},{"date":"15:37 31/03","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MU vs Swansea 21h00 ng\u00e0y 31/3 (Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/truc-tiep-mu-vs-swansea-21h00-ngay-313-ngoai-hang-anh-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80