adow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i danh \u201cSalah Messi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d hay \u201cRonaldo Ai C\u1eadp\u201d, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Salah h\u00e3y v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 ra m\u1eaft Liverpool n\u00e0y.</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta b\u1ef1c m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League: N\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh b\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao-172-171225.html\">Kevin De Bruyne</span>. \u0110\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1edfi v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah Liverpool 5-0 Watford\" title=\"Salah Liverpool 5-0 Watford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/nhieu-tru-cot-cua-liverpool-lo-ngai-salah-se-toi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah c\u1ee7a Liverpool x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng d\u1ea5y l\u00ean d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00fang h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u00ednh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u d\u00e2n \u00fd v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m nay. Mohamed Salah v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n th\u0103ng hoa, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd anh c\u00f2n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 mu\u00f4n ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a De Bruyne.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00fa poker si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1edbi Watford v\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft x\u1ed1i x\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Leo Messi, ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. \"Salah Messi Ai C\u1eadp\" - M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh m\u1ef9 mi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u0169ng th\u1eadt\u2026 nh\u1ee9c nh\u1ed1i l\u00e0m sao!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a ra so s\u00e1nh n\u00e0y mang h\u00e0m \u00fd ch\u00ednh y\u1ebfu \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f9a vui, hay t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch khen ng\u1ee3i v\u00e0 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, n\u00f3 c\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng song h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t trong s\u1ef1 l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-50-watford-172-182331.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/du-am-liverpool-50-watford.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-50-watford-172-182331.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Watford: C\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n Salah!</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f4i khi c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang xem Leo Messi \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u1eady. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ec1m h\u00e3m s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta khi mong m\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eebng c\u00f3 so s\u00e1nh g\u00ec h\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Salah \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a anh. C\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u0111\u00f4i ba m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n v\u1edbi Messi, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p m\u1edbi d\u00e1m m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n x\u1ebfp anh ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u00ean Barcelona.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi th\u00ec ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh kh\u1eadp khi\u1ec5ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng, v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u00e0m \u0111i\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Messi. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 v\u1eady th\u00f4i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mo Salah Messi Ai Cap hay mot su so sanh lo bich hinh anh 2\" title=\"Mo Salah Messi Ai C\u1eadp hay m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/mo-salah-messi-ai-cap-hay-mot-su-so-sanh-lo-bich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Salah Messi Ai C\u1eadp th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/barca-30-chelsea-show-dien-cho-rieng-thien-tai-messi-184-182107.html\">S\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Messi</span> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ec3u th\u1ecb \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng li\u00ean k\u1ebft m\u1ecdi m\u1eaft x\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Salah trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Salah kh\u00f4ng, hay \u00edt nh\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng khi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n trong t\u1ea7m ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. B\u00e1m bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00ean anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung phong, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 Salah Messi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, Salah \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 m\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho n\u00f3. V\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t v\u00f4 nh\u1ecb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u1eadt ra, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00ed \u00edt t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah nen duoc so sanh voi Ronaldo du rang van con rat khap khieng\" title=\"Salah n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u1eadp khi\u1ec5ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Salah-Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Salah Messi Ai C\u1eadp n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, ng\u00f4i sao Liverpool n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u1eadp khi\u1ec5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u00e0ng n\u0103m tr\u1eddi nay, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 hay sao, v\u1edbi kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u1edf b\u00ean c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-tro-lai-loi-khang-dinh-cua-nha-vua-180-180776.html\">\u00d4ng vua c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span> \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngang b\u1eb1ng Salah, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t trung phong truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, danh th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 theo th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng trong.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi, ch\u00ednh Ronaldo m\u1edbi l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n d\u00e0nh cho Salah. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0 Messi, Ronaldo hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1eabn h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh ngang. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c hay x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 h\u1ebft khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee9ng chung h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 v\u1edbi hai thi\u00ean t\u00e0i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t chia nhau 10 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua. V\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i danh \u201cMessi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d hay \u201cRonaldo Ai C\u1eadp\u201d, Salah h\u00e3y v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 ra m\u1eaft Liverpool n\u00e0y, ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o m\u1edd che c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Neymar, Griezmann hay Hazard.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng Salah Messi Ai C\u1eadp?</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-roger-federer-cua-gioi-bong-da-172-180122.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/13/mohamed-salah-roger-federer-cua-gioi-bong-da.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-roger-federer-cua-gioi-bong-da-172-180122.html\">Mohamed Salah: Roger Federer c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i sao Mohamed Salah c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft n\u00f3? V\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft Adam Bate \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Salah gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi tay v\u1ee3t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-nguoi-anh-hung-quoc-dan-ai-cap-172-176628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/31/mohamed-salah-nguoi-anh-hung-quoc-dan-ai-cap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-nguoi-anh-hung-quoc-dan-ai-cap-172-176628.html\">Mohamed Salah: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n Ai C\u1eadp</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed7i gi\u00e2y, m\u1ed7i l\u00fac, trong t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y, t\u1eebng pha t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng hay t\u1eebng c\u00fa s\u00fat. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Mohamed Salah, l\u00e0 l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho l\u00fd do tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-va-cuoc-hanh-huong-tim-ban-nga-172-175863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/20/mohamed-salah-va-cuoc-hanh-huong-tim-ban-nga.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-va-cuoc-hanh-huong-tim-ban-nga-172-175863.html\">Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00ecm b\u1ea3n ng\u00e3</span><br>\r\nL\u00fd do n\u00e0o gi\u00fap Mohamed Salah s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y? H\u00e3y nghe ch\u00ednh ch\u00e0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp chia s\u1ebb con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></body></html>",