-chelsea-chieu-mo-172-180989.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Radja Nainggolan</strong></span> trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Luciano Spalletti t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Nainggolan t\u1edbi Inter Milan \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh anh m\u1edbi cho bi\u1ebft ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi ti\u1ebft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Inter v\u00ec HLV Spalletti \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00f4i v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i\u201d, Nainggolan n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 1000 b\u00e0i b\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y qu\u00ean ch\u00fang \u0111i. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Spalletti, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1eddi Roma.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Radja Nainggolan khong den Chelsea va Inter hinh anh\" title=\"Radja Nainggolan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u00e0 Inter h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/7/radja-nainggolan-khong-den-chelsea-va-inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Radja Nainggolan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u00e0 Inter nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Inter, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o c\u1ea3, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean b\u00e1o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Inter, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-nainggolan-tu-choi-chuyen-toi-chelsea-172-181029.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Radja Nainggolan</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i Super League Trung Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t khi anh \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d, Nainggolan n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 k\u1ebb d\u1ed1i tr\u00e1 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 30 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi quan tr\u1ecdng. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Radja Nainggolan:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/44001-48582/033100\">Radja Nainggolan</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Radja Nainggolan tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-2-cau-thu-ma-hazard-muon-chelsea-chieu-mo-172-180989.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Hazard mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tien-ve-roma-than-nhien-livestream-canh-hut-thuoc-188-176968.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Roma th\u1ea3n nhi\u00ean livestream c\u1ea3nh h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u th\u1ea3 phanh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/as-roma-manh-hon-chelsea-184-171052.html\">Nainggolan: AS Roma m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/conte-thua-nhan-tung-san-may-quet-cua-roma-184-170920.html\">Conte th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn t\u1eebng s\u0103n m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nguoi-duoc-mu-nham-thay-carrick-172-168729.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U nh\u1eafm thay Carrick</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/soc-may-quet-radja-nainggolan-tuyen-bo-giai-nghe-tren-dt-bi-184-166983.html\">S\u1ed1c: \u201cM\u00e1y qu\u00e9t\u201d Radja Nainggolan tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 tr\u00ean \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-mourinho-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-voi-roma-176-164850.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Mourinho CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 