1\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay</u></strong></span></span>, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh Inter Milan vs Verona 20h00 ngay 313 Serie A 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Inter Milan vs Verona 20h00 ng\u00e0y 313 Serie A 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/int-ver.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter Milan vs Verona</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Inter Milan vs Verona: 1-0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Luciano Spalletti, g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf m\u1edbi lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Inter. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Inter \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Verona, ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u00fat xa b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i (kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn) c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Roma \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m k\u1ef3 th\u1ee9 hai, HLV Spalletti c\u0169ng ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Verona. Khi \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Spalletti \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Verona c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2016, m\u00e0 n\u00ean nh\u1edb Verona m\u00f9a 2015/16 \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng khi x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Serie A. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t Inter l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn t\u1eed chi\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p Milan (\u0111\u00e1 b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 27) gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, HLV Spalletti s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n chia s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Inter l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Verona. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Inter gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, ch\u1edb n\u00ean tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho Nerazzurri.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nInter s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Inter \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t khi h\u1ecd s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong khi Verona kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 5/6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. H\u00e3y tin th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Samir Handanovic s\u1ebd gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi cho Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"635","checkdouble":"183187"},{"date":"08:27 31/03","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus vs AC Milan 01h45 ng\u00e0y 1/4 (Serie A 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/31/nhan-dinh-juventus-vs-ac-milan-01h45-ngay-14-serie-a-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helveti